                <h2 style="color:var(--primary); margin:0 0 8px;">📜 Terms of Service</h2>
                <div
                    style="flex:1; overflow-y:auto; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.4); padding:14px; border-radius:8px; color:#ddd; font-size:0.85em; line-height:1.5; text-align:left;">
                    <p><strong>1. Acceptance of Terms.</strong> By using Aman Chat, you agree to these Terms of Service.
